sequenceDiagram
    participant Engine as Aeloop Loop
    participant Harness
    participant Context
    participant Prompt
    participant Model
    Engine->>Context: 请求任务上下文
    Context-->>Engine: memories + warnings + omitted
    Engine->>Prompt: role + context + task
    Prompt-->>Harness: persona + schema + context + task
    Harness->>Model: adapter.invoke(request)
    Model-->>Harness: raw response + usage + tool trace
    Harness-->>Engine: validated structured result
